description: Vendetta Mining Corp., a junior exploration company, acquires, explores for, and develops mineral properties in Australia. The company explores for lead, zinc, and silver deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Pegmont lead-zinc-silver deposit comprising three granted mining leases and 1 exploration permit covering an area of approximately 8,290 hectares located in northwest Queensland, Australia. The company was formerly known as Azincourt Resources Inc. and changed its name to Vendetta Mining Corp. in July 2010. Vendetta Mining Corp. was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
